data.description: Looking for horse property? Look no more! Home features 5.40 acres of fenced and cross fenced pastures. Three bedrooms, two full bathrooms and a utility/mud room that could be used as an additional bedroom, game room, dining room or living room. The kitchen has a beautiful backsplash and the stove, fridge, dishwasher and microwave will convey. Spacious combination living and dining area! The primary bedroom is large enough for a king bedroom set and has a private full bathroom. Second full bathroom is located in between the two additional bedrooms. Storage shed has been converted into a small "school house" and has LVP flooring and electricity. An additional open-face shed has electricity as well. Did I mention the two-story playhouse that also has electricity? Barn has separate fencing from the pastures and has two expansive hay storage bays. Pond can be found in the pastures. Sellers will require occupancy for 30-45 days after closing
